data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT [hc_clave_abonado], [hc_cod_trans] ,[cod_designacion] ,sum([hc_valor]) as hc_valor FROM [FACTURACION].[dbo].[fpac060] JOIN [FACTURACION].[dbo].[fpre020] ON [fpac060].[hc_cod_trans] = [fpre020].[cod_llave] WHERE HC_CICLO = @mes_facturacion AND hc_clave_abonado in (@clave) AND [hc_cod_trans] > 100 AND [hc_cod_trans] NOT IN (141,161,111,151) GROUP BY [hc_clave_abonado] ,[hc_cod_trans] ,[cod_designacion]

data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value: SELECT [InCMS].[dbo].[FPAC060_UNION].[hc_clave_abonado], coalesce(sum ([InCMS].[dbo].[FPAC060_UNION].[hc_valor]),0) as reactiva FROM [InCMS].[dbo].[FPAC060_UNION] WHERE HC_CICLO = @mes_facturacion AND [hc_cod_trans] IN (12 ,22,32,42,52,62,72) group by [hc_clave_abonado]

data.name: customSqlQuery3.Sql
data.value: SELECT clave ,mes,consumo FROM [FACTURACION].[dbo].[V_IMP_FAC_AC_V3] UNPIVOT ( consumo for mes in ([ENERO] ,[FEBRERO] ,[MARZO] ,[ABRIL] ,[MAYO] ,[JUNIO] ,[JULIO] ,[AGOSTO] ,[SEPTIEMBRE] ,[OCTUBRE] ,[NOVIEMBRE] ,[DICIEMBRE]) ) as pvtConsumoMes where clave in (SELECT IIF(CLAVE BETWEEN 3000000 AND 3999999, CLAVE-3000000, CLAVE ) FROM [SAGAV2].[dbo].[UniversoSAGA] where ( IIF(CLAVE BETWEEN 3000000 AND 3999999, CLAVE-3000000, CLAVE )) = @clave)
